        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7555/101283/7555_101283_000072_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7555",
        "content": "And a second cushion fell down.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7555_101283_000073_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7555/101283/7555_101283_000073_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7555",
        "content": "'Let them take their silliness home,' said the empress.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7555_101283_000077_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7555/101283/7555_101283_000077_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7555",
        "content": "When they reached the warlike expedition of the emperor three of the cushions fell down at once.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7555_105394_000000_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7555/105394/7555_105394_000000_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7555",
        "content": "CHAPTER fifteen DOUBT",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7555_105394_000001_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7555/105394/7555_105394_000001_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7555",
        "content": "Marguerite Blakeney had watched the slight sable clad figure of Chauvelin, as he worked his way through the ball room.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7555_105394_000002_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7555/105394/7555_105394_000002_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7555",
        "content": "Listlessly she sat in the small, still deserted boudoir, looking out through the curtained doorway on the dancing couples beyond: looking at them, yet seeing nothing, hearing the music, yet conscious of naught save a feeling of expectancy, of anxious, weary waiting.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7555_105394_000003_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7555/105394/7555_105394_000003_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7555",
        "content": "Her mind conjured up before her the vision of what was, perhaps at this very moment, passing downstairs.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7555_105394_000005_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7555/105394/7555_105394_000005_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7555",
        "content": "Ah! had Armand's life not been at stake! . . .",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7555_105394_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7555/105394/7555_105394_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7555",
        "content": "\"Faith! your ladyship must have thought me very remiss,\" said a voice suddenly, close to her elbow.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7555_105394_000006_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7555/105394/7555_105394_000006_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7555",
        "content": "\"I had a deal of difficulty in delivering your message, for I could not find Blakeney anywhere at first . . .\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7555_105394_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7555/105394/7555_105394_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7555",
        "content": "\"I did find him at last,\" continued Lord Fancourt, \"and gave him your message.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7555_105394_000008_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7555/105394/7555_105394_000008_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7555",
        "content": "He said that he would give orders at once for the horses to be put to.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7555_105394_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7555/105394/7555_105394_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7555",
        "content": "\"Ah!\" she said, still very absently, \"you found my husband, and gave him my message?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7555_105394_000010_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7555/105394/7555_105394_000010_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7555",
        "content": "I could not manage to wake him up at first.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7555_105394_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7555/105394/7555_105394_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7555",
        "content": "\"Thank you very much,\" she said mechanically, trying to collect her thoughts.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7555_105394_000016_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7555/105394/7555_105394_000016_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7555",
        "content": "Lord Fancourt was very attentive.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7555_105394_000016_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7555/105394/7555_105394_000016_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7555",
        "content": "She scarcely heard what he said, and suddenly startled him by asking abruptly,--",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7555_105394_000017_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7555/105394/7555_105394_000017_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7555",
        "content": "\"Lord Fancourt, did you perceive who was in the dining room just now besides Sir Percy Blakeney?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7555_105394_000018_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7555/105394/7555_105394_000018_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7555",
        "content": "\"Why does your ladyship ask?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7555_105394_000019_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7555/105394/7555_105394_000019_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7555",
        "content": "\"I know not . . .",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7555_105394_000019_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7555/105394/7555_105394_000019_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7555",
        "content": "Did you notice the time when you were there?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7555_105394_000020_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7555/105394/7555_105394_000020_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7555",
        "content": "\"It must have been about five or ten minutes past one. . . .",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7555_105394_000020_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7555/105394/7555_105394_000020_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7555",
        "content": "I wonder what your ladyship is thinking about,\" he added, for evidently the fair lady's thoughts were very far away, and she had not been listening to his intellectual conversation.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7555_105394_000021_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7555/105394/7555_105394_000021_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7555",
        "content": "But indeed her thoughts were not very far away: only one storey below, in this same house, in the dining room where sat Chauvelin still on the watch.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7555_105394_000021_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7555/105394/7555_105394_000021_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7555",
        "content": "Had he failed?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7555_105394_000021_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7555/105394/7555_105394_000021_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7555",
        "content": "For one instant that possibility rose before as a hope-the hope that the Scarlet Pimpernel had been warned by Sir Andrew, and that Chauvelin's trap had failed to catch his bird; but that hope soon gave way to fear.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7555_105394_000021_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7555/105394/7555_105394_000021_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7555",
        "content": "Had he failed?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7555_105394_000023_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7555/105394/7555_105394_000023_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7555",
        "content": "\"Shall I find out if your ladyship's coach is ready,\" he said at last, tentatively.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7555_105394_000025_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7555/105394/7555_105394_000025_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7555",
        "content": "But Lord Fancourt went, and still Chauvelin did not come.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7555_105394_000025_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7555/105394/7555_105394_000025_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7555",
        "content": "Oh! what had happened?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7555_105394_000028_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7555/105394/7555_105394_000028_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7555",
        "content": "Lord Grenville himself came presently to tell her that her coach was ready, and that Sir Percy was already waiting for her-ribbons in hand.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7555_105394_000033_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7555/105394/7555_105394_000033_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7555",
        "content": "The crowd was very great, some of the Minister's guests were departing, others were leaning against the banisters watching the throng as it filed up and down the wide staircase.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7555_105394_000035_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7555/105394/7555_105394_000035_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7555",
        "content": "\"What has happened, dear lady?\" he said, with affected surprise.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7555_105394_000035_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7555/105394/7555_105394_000035_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7555",
        "content": "\"Where? When?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7555_105394_000036_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7555/105394/7555_105394_000036_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7555",
        "content": "\"You are torturing me, Chauvelin.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
